    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to intel-vaapi-driver</title>

      <para>
         The <application>intel-vaapi-driver</application> package contains
         a VA API driver for Intel GPUs that are provided with Haswell CPUs
         and earlier.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

